704381f-a.title: Brooklyn: Florence Avenue - Gerritsen Avenue
704381f-a.text:
Florence Ave., south side, west from Gerritsen Ave. In the foreground,
is a view of St. James' Lutheran Church.
June 23, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
